                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#iiv(erso)" facs="003">Fol. iiv(erso)</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1031VirginAndChild">Virgin and Child</ref>. Colorful, ornate ḥaräg above miniature</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#35v" facs="038">Fol. 35v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1005Crucifixion">Crucifixion of Jesus</ref> with captions <q>“[abbreviation for] Jesus of Nazareth, King of the Jews” (top), “Maryam” (lower left), and “John”</q> (right)</desc></decoNote>
