                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d6"><locus target="#120r" facs="122">Fol. 120r</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1049Resurrection">Resurrection of Jesus</ref>, raising Adam and Eve. Two evil men below (showing one eye). Colorful, ornate ḥaräg above miniature with captions <q>“[abbreviation for] Jesus Christ, King of the Jews” (on banner), “How God rose from the Dead; Adam and Eve” (left), and “Jews” (two times at bottom)</q></desc></decoNote>
